205390028.Title: Premier 24 in. 2.97 cu. ft. Electric Range in Black
205390028.Description: Ideal for kitchenettes, small kitchens, studio apartments or any meal-prep area with space constraints, this 24 in. Freestanding Electric Range from Premier is a dependable cooking machine for any chef. It has one 8 in. burner and three 6 in. burners to handle an assortment of pots and pans, while a spacious 2.97 cu. ft. oven with two adjustable-height racks is at your disposal for baking at temperatures up to 500°F. A broil setting is also available to cook items under intense heat in close proximity to the upper heating element for browning and searing. Color: Black.

314155350.Title: Summit Appliance 20 in. 2.3 cu. ft. Slide-in Electric Range in Black
314155350.Description: The REX2051BRT is a 220-Volt electric range sized at just under 20 in. wide in a jet black finish. The versatile design includes a removable 2 in. high stainless steel backguard, allowing you the choice of a standard range style or a slide-in look with a flat surface that allows you to better integrate the unit with your own backsplash design. The smooth ceramic glass surface includes four 1200-Watt 6-1/2 in. elements, with a hot surface indicator light for added safety. Inside, the REX2051BRT features a large 2.3 cu. ft. oven made from durable porcelain enamel. The waist-high broiler function is easy to use, with slide-out oven racks that can be adjusted in four different glide positions for the best fit. We include a small two-piece porcelain broiler tray with a grill cover. The large oven window and interior light make it easy to monitor your cooking. With its slim fit, the REX2051BRT is the perfect choice for smaller kitchens with full cooking needs. Additional choices are available in 24 in. wide fits.

309372256.Title: PREMIUM 24 in. 2.7 cu. ft. Electric Range in Black with Stainless Steel Door
309372256.Description: PREMIUM's 24 in. 2.7 cu. ft. Electric Range in Black with Stainless Steel Door is the perfect appliance for your apartment, condo or office kitchen. The stylish black color with stainless steel accents livens up any kitchen and matches any decor. Just as in larger units there is an in-door window and oven light to allow users to check on food while it is cooking, 2 adjustable wire racks, a broiler tray and grid included, and a handy removable storage drawer. With its small footprint, it conserves space while providing all the functionality you need to cook healthy meals at home.

202988065.Title: Premier 24 in. 2.97 cu. ft. Electric Range in Black
202988065.Description: The Premier 24 in. Freestanding Electric Range brings you the features you need while accommodating a smaller kitchen space. All Premier ranges come with an Exclusive Lifetime Warranty on all Top Burner Elements - Your assurance that you are purchasing a top quality product. Equipped with a lift-up cook top and support rod, this range is a cinch to keep clean. Safety features like the Surface Indicator Light, will let you know at a glance if cooktop burners are on. Color: Black.
